{"id":216950,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/03/维权网-成都独立候选人王荣文被非法关押17天获赔/","date":"2012-03-23T00:09:00Z","modified":"2012-03-23T00:09:00Z","title":"维权网 | 成都独立候选人王荣文被非法关押17天获赔偿1500元（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span></span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a>（维权网信息员刘天天报道）据成都独立候选人王荣文称：她在选举日被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多人绑架后，被关黑监狱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>天，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日被释放回来，当即去找街道办事处书记赵明波索赔，赵书记让王荣文第二天再来找综治办主任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>下午，王荣文到街道办事处去找青羊区少城街办综治办主任李双全，李主任很爽快的就给了王荣文</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1500</span><span>元钱。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">       </span></div>\n<div><span>王荣文说：自己因上访每年都被非法关押，对于这种由政府违法造成的心里伤害是无法弥补的，而且即使根据现行国家赔偿法规定，每天的赔偿也因该是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">130</span><span>多元一天，关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>天赔偿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1500</span><span>元，显然不够。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">       </span></div>\n<div><span>王荣文表示：正打算针对青羊区少城街办历年来对她实施非法关押的事情提起国家赔偿，如果少城街办拒赔，将依法向人民法院提起国家赔偿诉讼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">       </span></div>\n<div><span>据王荣文说：在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>投票日那天，当警察在对她进行录像拍照时她也用自己的手机把当时对她实施监视和选举的情况进行拍摄，并且保留了下来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>以下是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日当天王荣文拍摄的照片</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-y7wi8koEzE0/T2XVN2Hg6PI/AAAAAAAAF68/Evx4SWhgA24/s1600/2%E6%9C%8827%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%A5%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-y7wi8koEzE0/T2XVN2Hg6PI/AAAAAAAAF68/Evx4SWhgA24/s1600/2%E6%9C%8827%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%A5%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8.jpg\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2月27日投票点无人来投票</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dns1XuU1Vak/T2XVRFvJSVI/AAAAAAAAF7E/5BBANVgEplQ/s1600/%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2qq%E8%BD%A6%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%BC%E6%B2%BB%E5%8A%9E%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E6%9D%8E%E5%8F%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%E5%9D%90%E7%9A%84%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E4%BB%96%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%89%E5%90%8D%E5%9B%BD%E4%BF%9D%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E6%8B%BF%E7%9D%80%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%92%8C%E7%85%A7%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E8%A1%97%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E5%92%8C%E6%8B%8D%E7%85%A7.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dns1XuU1Vak/T2XVRFvJSVI/AAAAAAAAF7E/5BBANVgEplQ/s1600/%E7%BB%BF%E8%89%B2qq%E8%BD%A6%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%BC%E6%B2%BB%E5%8A%9E%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E6%9D%8E%E5%8F%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%E5%9D%90%E7%9A%84%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E4%BB%96%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E8%BF%98%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%89%E5%90%8D%E5%9B%BD%E4%BF%9D%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98%E6%8B%BF%E7%9D%80%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%92%8C%E7%85%A7%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E8%A1%97%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E5%92%8C%E6%8B%8D%E7%85%A7.jpg\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>绿色车上国保拿着摄像机对行人摄像</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UU2uB83L918/T2XVT9-tcFI/AAAAAAAAF7M/bqSXj7OYBT8/s1600/%E6%B4%BE%E5%87%BA%E6%89%80%E6%89%80%E9%95%BF%E6%B1%AA%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%8C%E5%92%8C%E4%B8%A4%E5%90%8D%E5%9B%BD%E4%B